net.sf.mmm.client.ui.api.media

Interface MediaDescriptor

  • All Superinterfaces:
    AttributeReadStringTitle, AttributeReadTitle<String>, AttributeReadUrl
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    AudioDescriptor, VideoDescriptor
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AudioDescriptorBean, MediaDescriptorBean, VideoDescriptorBean

    public interface MediaDescriptor
extends AttributeReadUrl, AttributeReadStringTitle
    This is the abstract interface for a descriptor of multi-media-data. It is either an AudioDescriptor for audio tracks or a VideoDescriptor for videos. You can either implement these interfaces directly by your business objects or use the provided java beans.
    Since:
    1.0.0
    Author:
    Joerg Hohwiller (hohwille at users.sourceforge.net)
